headline: Gemini Bioproducts, LLC Acquires Selected Fetal Bovine Serum (FBS) Product Rights and Inventory from Bio-Techne
summary: Gemini Bioproducts, LLC ("GeminiBio"), a leading supplier of cell culture reagents and process liquids, and a portfolio company of BelHealth Investment Partners, LLC ("BelHealth"), a Florida-based healthcare private equity firm, today announced the acquisition of selected fetal bovine serum (FBS) product rights and inventory from Bio-Techne (NASDAQ: TECH).
